{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, we investigated the impact or feature reliability (here functional connectivity) on our results.",
    "As the length of the resting state time-course has been shown to influence the reliability of function connectivity 22, 58, 59, we reduced the amount of resting state data used for calculating it and repeated all predictions.",
    "In the main analyses of the HCP-A, all 4 resting sessions from both days were used (22 min and 44 s).",
    "To reduce feature reliability, functional connectivity was then calculated using both sessions from each day separately (13 min and 22 s) and lastly, to mirror the UKB acquisition protocol, only the very first session acquired in the anterior-to-posterior direction on day one (6 min and 41 s) was used for calculating functional connectivity.",
    "All control analyses are presented in the supplemental material."
  ]
}